Package: fixated
Title: Analyze Eye Movement Data from Eye Trackers
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bernhard", "Angele", , "bernhard.angele@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Read raw samples and fixation/saccade events from CSV or ASC files
    saved by eye trackers (e.g., SR Research EyeLink). Optionally detect fixations
    using dispersion-based algorithms, clean and merge fixations, eliminate
    outliers, read regions of interest for words in sentences from a CSV, and
    compile word-based eye-movement measures such as first fixation duration,
    gaze duration, go-past time, and total viewing time.
